                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature enters the prayer room.</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The abbot's spirit appears and begins to channel powerful ki energy. One round later, the room fills with a powerful kinetic storm, dealing [[/r 3d10+15 # electricity damage]]{3d10+15 electricity damage} and [[/r 3d10+15 # force damage]]{3d10+15 force damage} to all creatures in the room. Creatures in the room must attempt a <span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-traits=\"haunt\" data-pf2-label=\"\" data-pf2-dc=\"37\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Reflex</span> save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage and becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Deafened]{Deafened} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage, [[/r 2d8 # persistent electricity damage]]{2d8} @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Persistent Damage]{Persistent Electricity Damage}, and becomes deafened for 1 minute.</p>"
